description:
This course provides quick and strong foundation to SAP BW 7.4 Modeling for beginners, it is not complete BW Modeling course.  For complete BW Modeling course join for "SAP BW 7.4 Zero to Hero". 

  • What is SAP BW ?
  • What is DataWareHouse?
  • What is DataWareHouse Work Bench?
  • What is Modeling?
  • What is InfoArea?
  • What is InfoObject Catalog?
  • What is InfoObjects and Types?
  • How to Load Master Data?
  • How to Load Transaction Data?
title: SAP BW 7.4 Modeling - For Dummies
